    ", where ψ⟩ | is a pure state of interest and ρ exp ̂ is the exper- imental mixed state.",
    "For digital devices studying deep circuits, the fidelity can be estimated by means of the linear cross-entropy 2, 12, a cross-correlation between measurement outcomes of an experiment and an exact classical simulation.",
